== Days of Kinoto-Ushi == === Calendar Annotations === Days of Kinoto-Ushi are associated with the following annotations in the {{ill|Japanese calendar|ja|暦注下段|12=draft|12=draft}}: * {{ill|Kyoueibi|ja|凶会日|12=draft|12=draft}} – applicable in the 3rd and 10th lunar months. * {{ill|Gokubi|ja|五墓日|12=draft|12=draft}} – applies to individuals whose {{ill|Na-in|ja|納音|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to the Wood element. * {{ill|Shinkichinichi|ja|神吉日|12=draft|12=draft}} – auspicious for spiritual matters. == See Also == * {{prefix}} * {{intitle}}
