nts|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=conquest|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Conquest in Five Elements|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Conquest in Five Elements|qq=}} (Wood conquers Earth).
==Pronunciation== PronounciationYin Wood Ox
<!-- == * Yin Wood Ox (乙丑) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): yǐchǒu ** Cantonese (Jyutping): jat1 cau2 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi: きのとうし (kinoto-ushi) ***Onyomi: おつぼくのうし (otsuboku-no-ushi) ***Onyomi: おつちゅう (otsuchū) ** Korean (Revised Romanization): eulchuk ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Ất Sửu
--> ==Years of Yin Wood Ox== Gregorian calendar years that leave a remainder of 5 when divided by 60 are years of Kinoto-Ushi.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Kinoto-Ushi''' |- ! [[1st Millennium]] !! [[2nd Millennium]] !! [[3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[5]] * [[65]] * [[125]] * [[185]] * [[245]] * [[305]] * [[365]] * [[425]]
* [[485]] * [[545]] * [[605]] * [[665]] * [[725]] * [[785]] * [[845]] * [[905]] * [[965]] | * [[1025]] * [[1085]] * [[1145]] * [[1205]] * [[1265]] * [[1325]] * [[1385]] * [[1445]] * [[1505]] * [[1565]] * [[1625]] * [[1685]] * [[1745]] * [[1805]] * [[1865]] * [[1925]] * [[1985]] | * [[2045]] * [[2105]] * [[2165]] * [[2225]] * [[2285]] * [[2345]] * [[2405]] * [[2465]] * [[2525]] * [[2585]] * [[2645]] * [[2705]] * [[2765]] * [[2825]] * [[2885]] * [[2945]] |}
==Months of Yin Wood Ox== The twelfth month (December) of Gregorian calendar years ending in 3 or 8 (Heavenly Stems 癸 or 戊) corresponds to Kinoto-Ushi months. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or [[:en:Solar term|Solar terms]] (from [[:en:Xiaohan|Shōkan]] to the day before [[:en:Lichun|Risshun]]) in traditional contexts.
==Days of Yin Wood Ox== === Calendar Annotations === Days of Kinoto-Ushi are associated with the following annotations in the {{ill|Japanese calendar|ja|暦注下段|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese calendar|qq=}}: * {{ill|Kyoueibi|ja|凶会日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyoueibi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyoueibi|qq=}} – applicable in the 3rd and 10th lunar months. * {{ill|Gokubi|ja|五墓日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gokubi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gokubi|qq=}} – applies to individuals whose {{ill|Na-in|ja|納音|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Na-in|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Na-in|qq=}} corresponds to the Wood element. * {{ill|Shinkichinichi|ja|神吉日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinkichinichi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinkichinichi|qq=}} – auspicious for spiritual matters. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
