=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|lt=Earth (土)}}, creating a relationship of {{ill|Conquest in Five Elements|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=conquest|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Conquest in Five Elements|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Conquest in Five Elements|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q218652}} (Wood conquers Earth).

